    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Yes my website shows a webpage for each item in hierarchical menu. I can configure google analytics for all urls but that has some disadvantages.\n1. Google likes clean and simple urls\n2. Sending google a url like .../...?q=w&p=0&dFR[brand][0]=XX&dFR[brand][1]=YY&.... does not seem a good opinion. This will also increase page views because this will send 5 views for a search like \"q=white\"\n\nMaybe turbolinks can be a solution for this?\n",
