    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@tecmusti Revisiting this issue I will try to get it right:\n- You want to have pages like /dresses, when accessed should display dresses\n- You want the links in your hierarchicalRefinementList(s) to go through /dresses/red\n\nTo solve this, you would only need to be able to provide a hook (function) here: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/6291bfc47e9b91a0c8ea947355c9f68851187d20/src/lib/url-sync.js#L79\n\nIf this is all you need then why not submit a pull request? As an example, I recently added a way to provide a different History.state at each url render (urlbar/refinementList urls): https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/commit/989856cb12c797c881301963c118e2d2b10aa63b\n\nOtherwise I will try to have a go at it. Please confirm to me that this is the only need that would be required to you.\n",
